ACCESS PROTECTION
-----------------

ip ssh time-out 60
ip ssh logging events
crypto key generate rsa usage-keys label SSH modulus 4096
ip ssh rsa keypair-name SSH
ip ssh version 2
ip scp server enable
ip access-list standard SSH
permit 100.0.0.1 0.0.0.0
deny   any log
line vty 0 2
access-class SSH in
no ip domain-name

GENERAL SECURITY CONFIGURATION
------------------------------

ip tftp blocksize 8192
no service tcp-small-servers
no service udp-small-servers
no service finger
no service config
no cdp run
no ip http server
no ip http secure-server
no ip bootp server
no service dhcp
no snmp-server enable traps
no snmp-server
no ip source-route
service tcp-keepalives-in
service tcp-keepalives-out
no service pad
privilege exec level 15 enable
ip arp proxy disable

LINE CONFIGURATION
-----------------

line vty 0 2
login local
transport input ssh
transport output ssh
exec-timeout 3 0
logging synchronous

line cons 0
login local
exec-timeout 3 0
transport preferred none
logging synchronous

line vty 3 X
login
no exec
transport input none
transport output none

AUTHENTICATION LOGGING
----------------------

login on-failure log
login on-success log

BRUTE FORCE PROTECTION
----------------------

login block-for 300 attempts 3 within 120
login delay 2

LOG CONFIGURATION
-----------------

service timestamps log datetime localtime show-timezone
archive
log config
logging enable
hidekeys
notify syslog
logging size 1000
logging buffered 64000
logging console notifications
logging monitor notifications

NULL0 INTERFACE DEACTIVATION (L3 ONLY)
--------------------------------------

interface Null0
no ip unreachables
no ip source-route

VLAN AND VLAN 1 INTERFACE CONFIGURATION (L2 ONLY)
-------------------------------------------------

vlan 666
name QUARANTINE
shutdown

vlan 999
name NATIVE

int vlan 1
shutdown
no ip redirects
no ip unreachables
no ip mask-reply
no ip proxy-arp
no ip route-cache
no ip mroute-cache

L2-SPECIFIC CONFIGURATION
-------------------------

vtp mode transparent
